snippet: After Prime Minister Erdogan’s order to clear the park that has been the scene of two weeks of protests, The Times’s Sebnem Arsu tells Marcus Mabry that Turkey and Turkish politics will never be the same.
abstract: After Prime Minister Erdogan’s order to clear the park that has been the scene of two weeks of protests, The Times’s Sebnem Arsu tells Marcus Mabry that Turkey and Turkish politics will never be the same.

headline.main: Why the Protests Have Changed Turkey Forever
